  "texts": [
    "Given a paragraph of a news article, identify zero or more out of 23 persuasion techniques used (see S1 Appendix for a detailed list of the techniques).",
    "The set of techniques represents an extension of the taxonomy used in previous SemEval datasets [26, 28].",
    "The task additionally provides 6 high-level categories that subsume similar persuasion techniques.",
    "Although the task is paragraph level, each of the articles has at least one labelled paragraph.",
    "It should be noted that three of the systems that participated in the original SemEval-2023 Task 3 [15] evaluation exercise used adapters."
  ],
